  "instructions": [
    "Heat a tablespoon of oil in a pan, add minced garlic and ginger.",
    "Stir until the garlic turns light golden brown.",
    "Add plum tomatoes to the pan, reduce heat and simmer for about 5 minutes or until they soften.",
    "Pour in the soy sauce, rice vinegar, sugar, and water. Stir well and cook for another minute.",
    "Fold in the canned nuts and let it cook for an additional 2-3 minutes.",
    "Serve hot as a dessert with sliced avocado on top."
